race.comment: UNPLANNED REVOLT (4) is lightly raced and unlike most has plenty of upside still. Runner-up two back then a close-up fifth in a tougher line-up last time. Trained here and looks a top chance this company. Stablemate COSMOS FACTORY (8) was having his first run for the new yard and ran a big race. Sat on speed and fought on well when runner-up and is surely improved for this. First try at his new home track but hard to beat again on the latest. SMILING ASSASSIN (3) is a veteran who has been racing in much tougher company. Worth noting he won only try this course and distance. Gets a chance to improve.  NORTHERN BARRAGE (7) finished seventh, beaten 8 lengths, last start over 2200m at Hamilton. Has the ability and looks one of the chances.
